{"type":"click","text":"A. Product Archive\n        \n          \n            \n              Product Ecosystem\n              An integrated structure that turns field data into stronger decisions.\n            \n            \n          \n          \n            \n              FWBM\n              Household resilience measurement at institutional scale.\n              Validated Data / Structured Analytics / Decision Infrastructure\n            \n            \n              FuzzyOwl\n              Makes visible how variables shape decisions and interventions.\n              Relational Mapping / AI Analytics / Scenario Simulation\n            \n            \n              EconImpact\n              Deterministic value creation and AI-based reporting.\n              Valuation Engine / AI Reporting / Expert Customization\n            \n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      Product Archive\n      Reads like a premium institutional catalog. Strongest editorial feel, easiest to scale, and clearly different from the previous sections.","choice":"product-a","id":null,"timestamp":1774444344802}
